title: GSSSB Notification 2025 - Apply Online for 138 Physiotherapist Posts
description: The Gujarat Secondary Service Selection Board (GSSSB) has officially released the notification to fill the vacancies of 138 Physiotherapist Posts. Interested and eligibile candidates can use this opportunity to apply for these posts before the last date of application. Candidates who have completed their Any Degree, BPT can apply for the GSSSB Notification 2025 . The interested applicants can apply in online mode. Here we have mentioned the education details, age limit, selection process, app...
